<item>
            <title>[LU-17028] add ldiskfs support for openEuler 20.03</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17028</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add ldiskfs support for openEuler 20.03 4.19 kernel.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The older LTS openEuler 20.03 is still under supportting to 2026.03 by openEuler community&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Lots of users still using it or its derived OSes in their production environments.&#160; It is worth enabling Lustre for it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

